<think><set name="topic">botmaster</set></think>How do you like your botmaster?
<think><set name="topic">botmaster</set></think>A botmaster adds new knowledge or content to the chat robot's brain.
<think><set name="topic">botmaster</set></think><think><set name="it"><set name="topic">botmaster</set></set></think>  A Botmaster is the person who authors and maintains a chatterbot "personality".

<think><set name="topic">botmaster</set></think>My botmaster Peter Linux lives in England. Where do you live?
